{"tid":1907574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國戰線，功能組別，why not both?","createTime":"2020-03-02T16:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T16:46:35.000Z","uid":22607,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e266004bbd1a9b033de81cf204c465a362d71f92","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:42:23.000Z","msg":"不如咁講啦<br />\n我覺得兩邊都諗得好撚理想<br />\n<br />\n一邊覺得功能組別一定過到半贏硬 <br />\n狗共唔出拿渣招 唔DQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一邊就覺得功能組別冇撚柒用 主張體制外抗爭 <br />\n覺得美帝一定會幫拖打低邪惡政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以嘈得好激烈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係其實兩者係mutually non-exclusive架喎<br />\n我地應該做嘅野係要求泛民<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用行動換選票<br />\n唔好比佢地覺得我地老馮要含撚投佢地</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講衰啲 泛民係過去8個月 特別係運動早期作出嘅種種貢獻<br />\n某程度上係因為想爭取選票 <br />\n佢地知民意係黃 佢地唔歸邊就唔會有支持者 唔會有工開 <br />\n宜家都一樣<br />\n我地要比泛民知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢地想狗衝選功能組別係有前提<br />\n前提係佢地要幫我地向美國繼續游說 盡力令美國幫我地達成普選</span><br />\n（利申：我唔覺得美國會道德潔癖屌鳩我地玩功能組別）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n強調！！！<br />\n想攞選票係有條件！！！<br />\n佢地一定要分配人手去美國戰線<br />\n我地先會支持佢地進攻功能組別！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同意請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10148ebcc45db5cfbdd250743307617b51a79b4d","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b9eef49b58e1f5ab3ce2d33438aec801e26e25d","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1d0fcb6742d4c1169276c79ce6d761d4b29b62b6","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e2499d19935ce725461949719255a8056157184","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:43:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0833edc3ff508fc4cf946369d7090ec2a835141a","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e79b28eb804f845e5ccc4b84cada4e3cb531e87","tid":1907574,"uid":88823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"全部戰線都要打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79dbb98105cd6fa9a07b733384d5e43d3dcf4ee9","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:45:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"164005af0823e1ff3d898f06c07f3b1eb5ae96a0","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e67452bae978a840e7d33f101101eb0777f21b71","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:46:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1cae08f1eaf4589e73166d999138574e1518a3d2","tid":1907574,"uid":22607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}